WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:45.280
Lin Mo.

00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:46.880
Wait for me.

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:50.120
People can't go out at night in Luoxian Town,

00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:51.040
especially women.

00:00:51.040 --> 00:00:51.880
Why did you come here?

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:52.600
Nonsense.

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:53.920
How could I leave you alone?

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:54.850
Go back quickly.

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:56.640
Someone needs to watch over Han Qingyun.

00:00:56.640 --> 00:00:57.920
If the protagonist of your book fails,

00:00:57.920 --> 00:00:59.600
it's useless even if we solve the monster problem.

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:00.880
Then go back with me.

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:01.880
Su Ning,

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:03.440
please stop making a scene right now.

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:04.879
Either you go back with me,

00:01:04.879 --> 00:01:05.960
or I go with you.

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:08.760
Your Majesty.

00:01:08.760 --> 00:01:09.720
Something happened.

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:10.580
What happened?

00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:11.480
Han Qingyun

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.610
used the distress talisman I gave him.

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:15.600
While the bell is still ringing,

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:18.260
quickly use your magic to deduce the situation.

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:23.120
It's the pharmacy owner from earlier today.

00:01:23.120 --> 00:01:24.640
Taking advantage of our departure,

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:25.640
he ambushed them.

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:27.680
Honey.

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:29.920
Han Qingyun is really important.

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:31.580
We can't afford any mistakes.

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:34.000
Then I'll let Wancai go with you.

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:34.720
No need.

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:36.680
I'm just going to investigate the clues and rules,

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:37.560
not to fight.

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:38.080
After I'm done,

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:38.800
I'll go find you.

00:01:38.800 --> 00:01:39.680
Then stay safe.

00:01:44.759 --> 00:01:45.289
Let's go.

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:46.080
Yes.

00:01:53.479 --> 00:01:54.720
My time is limited.

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:55.960
Make a decision quickly.

00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:56.759
Sorry.

00:01:56.759 --> 00:01:58.600
I don't work with demons.

00:01:58.759 --> 00:01:59.720
You'd better

00:01:59.720 --> 00:02:01.980
go into my Demon-Refining Banner first.

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:05.200
The bell has stopped.

00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:07.280
I knew you were waiting for this.

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:08.479
Keep setting off the fireworks.

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:09.320
This thing.

00:02:09.320 --> 00:02:10.080
All you want.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:13.640
Let's go.

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:14.920
Go.

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:21.660
It's a ghost marriage.

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:34.360
Go.

00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:36.000
This way.

00:03:08.200 --> 00:03:09.400
How is this possible?

00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:12.280
How could a ghost marriage and a funeral happen on the same night?

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:13.610
Boss, what should we do?

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:18.360
It must be the bell

00:03:18.520 --> 00:03:21.780
that changed the rules of the Lin Mansion and Luoxian Town.

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:22.650
Run that way.

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:24.400
Hurry!

00:03:30.920 --> 00:03:31.600
Run!

00:03:31.600 --> 00:03:32.360
Run!

00:03:43.160 --> 00:03:44.040
The Soul-Stealing Bell!

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:44.970
Cover your ears!

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:04.880
Damn.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.660
Protected by the dragon aura!

00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:13.480
Master.

00:04:13.640 --> 00:04:15.900
There is something wrong with that bell.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:16.959
Your Majesty.

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:18.160
We have no magic power.

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:19.890
We can't resist this artifact!

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:23.800
Don't enter its range.

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:25.080
I'll go stop them.

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:37.680
Give Han Xiaoying to the ghost wedding procession quickly.

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:39.610
They will leave once they have her.

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:53.720
Han Xiaoying.

00:04:53.760 --> 00:04:54.690
Wake up quickly.

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:58.880
Why?

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:02.120
Why didn't the ghost wedding procession come for her?

00:05:04.880 --> 00:05:05.540
Liu Wancai.

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:09.160
Xiaoying.

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:11.370
Don't get yourself killed.

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:15.640
Xiaoying.

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:16.560
Are you okay?

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:24.840
Master.

00:05:25.400 --> 00:05:26.200
Your Majesty.

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:33.159
Your Majesty.

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:34.480
Wait.

00:05:47.960 --> 00:05:48.480
Wait.

00:05:48.920 --> 00:05:49.200
Your Majesty.

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:50.760
The ghost marriage procession will drain the life force of outsiders.

00:05:50.760 --> 00:05:52.159
They will turn into mummies.

00:05:52.159 --> 00:05:53.890
We need to think of another way.

00:06:01.880 --> 00:06:02.520
Boss.

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:03.120
Go.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:03.960
This way.

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:39.360
Damn it.

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:44.360
Damn it.

00:06:45.320 --> 00:06:46.800
This isn't my first marriage.

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:48.000
Don't block me.

00:06:53.640 --> 00:06:56.200
Can someone please open the door?

00:06:57.240 --> 00:06:59.760
It's an emergency!

00:06:59.760 --> 00:07:00.560
Young Master.

00:07:08.520 --> 00:07:09.120
No.

00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:10.690
I can't die here.

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:12.120
Steal the Beams.

00:07:12.120 --> 00:07:12.650
Activate

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:26.920
skill, Steal the Beams.

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:28.440
Upgraded to Grafting.

00:07:28.440 --> 00:07:29.560
Can be cast remotely

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:30.880
with a 20-meter range.

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:32.480
Excellent.

00:07:35.640 --> 00:07:36.400
Who?

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:37.930
Who threw the firecracker?

00:07:38.760 --> 00:07:39.640
Young Master.

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:45.760
Young Master,

00:07:45.760 --> 00:07:46.159
how...

00:07:46.159 --> 00:07:47.360
how did you get here?

00:07:47.760 --> 00:07:49.120
You are...

00:07:49.320 --> 00:07:50.440
Mo Xiaolan?

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:53.040
Prompt:

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:54.440
Demon type updated.

00:07:54.440 --> 00:07:55.120
Wood Demon.

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.360
Weakness: Fire.

00:07:56.640 --> 00:07:58.040
My maid is a demon.

00:07:58.440 --> 00:08:00.320
It seems I can only sense the demon type

00:08:00.320 --> 00:08:01.920
when it exposes its demonic magic.

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:02.560
Young Master,

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:03.160
do you...

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:06.600
do you remember?

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:08.760
I haven't completely remembered.

00:08:08.760 --> 00:08:09.320
Lin Mo,

00:08:09.320 --> 00:08:10.080
step aside.

00:08:10.080 --> 00:08:10.920
Don't interfere with my demon catching.

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:11.400
Wait.

00:08:12.880 --> 00:08:14.400
I'll trade a rule

00:08:15.080 --> 00:08:16.210
for you to let her go.

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:18.360
Are you joking?

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:19.840
Do you know how much

00:08:19.840 --> 00:08:21.440
a Wood Demon's core is worth?

00:08:21.800 --> 00:08:22.600
Young Master,

00:08:22.640 --> 00:08:23.880
hide over there.

00:08:24.280 --> 00:08:25.340
I'll deal with her.

00:08:33.280 --> 00:08:34.000
No way.

00:08:34.120 --> 00:08:35.039
Not again.

00:08:54.560 --> 00:08:54.800
Young Master.

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:55.360
Let me go.

00:08:55.520 --> 00:08:56.320
Let Young Master go.

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:56.760
Get lost.

00:08:56.760 --> 00:08:57.640
Please,

00:08:57.920 --> 00:08:59.050
let Young Master go.

00:09:00.040 --> 00:09:00.840
Xiaolan.

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:02.480
Young Master.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.360
Xiaolan.

00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:05.520
Xiaolan.

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:08.800
Hold on tight.

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:11.520
If I knew this was how I'd die,

00:09:11.520 --> 00:09:12.240
I'd rather have been

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.120
sucked dry by that tree demon just now.

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:15.160
Damn it.

00:09:15.760 --> 00:09:17.480
Getting a bride through a ghost marriage,

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:18.560
who sucks people's vital essence...

00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:20.080
What kind of game is this?

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:21.760
Could it be

00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:24.120
that we're the dowry?

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:25.840
If you don't figure something out soon,

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:28.360
all these mortal men will be drained of their yang energy,

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:30.020
including your young master.

00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:31.320
I'm fine.

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:32.720
I can hold on.

00:09:32.960 --> 00:09:35.090
The sedan chair must take in two women.

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:36.760
Young Master, let go!

00:09:36.760 --> 00:09:38.280
Otherwise, you will die.

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:39.440
I won't let go.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:45.600
Lin Mo, let go!

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:47.560
Otherwise, you will all die.

00:09:47.960 --> 00:09:48.760
I told you to let go.

00:09:48.760 --> 00:09:50.090
Why are you so stubborn?

00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:51.520
Let go!

00:09:51.640 --> 00:09:52.280
Miss.

00:09:52.640 --> 00:09:53.900
What is your last name?

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:56.040
Do I know you well?

00:09:56.040 --> 00:09:57.240
My last name is Chu.

00:09:57.280 --> 00:09:59.210
Chu Xiao'er, Princess of Beijing.

00:09:59.240 --> 00:09:59.760
Lin Mo.

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:01.440
Find a way into the Lin residence to save me.

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.700
There will be a reward.

00:10:11.520 --> 00:10:12.560
Young master.

00:10:46.760 --> 00:10:47.760
Qi Recovery Pill.

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:49.080
Take it quickly.

00:10:56.360 --> 00:10:57.360
I ask, you answer.

00:10:57.480 --> 00:10:58.880
I'll let you die quickly.

00:10:59.640 --> 00:11:00.640
If I die,

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:03.020
you will never see your master again.

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:06.880
My patience is limited.

00:11:06.880 --> 00:11:08.920
Where did the ghost marriage procession go?

00:11:08.920 --> 00:11:10.360
The Lin family is holding a ghost marriage.

00:11:10.360 --> 00:11:12.120
Of course they returned to the Lin mansion.

00:11:12.120 --> 00:11:13.560
How do we enter the Lin mansion?

00:11:13.560 --> 00:11:14.960
If you want to enter the Lin mansion,

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:16.690
take me to see the young master.

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:22.600
[Prompt]

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:25.660
Strength and speed have been significantly improved.

00:11:27.040 --> 00:11:28.360
I feel like I am now

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.320
terrifyingly strong.

00:11:29.320 --> 00:11:30.320
Thanks, brother.

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:32.800
You just recovered.

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:34.460
Why are you risking your life?

00:11:34.880 --> 00:11:37.010
He also hasn't paid the final balance.

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:49.160
I thought it was just catching an ordinary demon,

00:11:49.160 --> 00:11:50.420
but I didn't expect...

00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:52.560
This trip is so dangerous.

00:11:53.320 --> 00:11:54.360
You two brothers,

00:11:54.720 --> 00:11:57.160
I will definitely bring the money to your families.

00:11:57.160 --> 00:11:58.090
Second Brother.

00:11:58.160 --> 00:12:00.560
This is what living on the edge is like.

00:12:00.640 --> 00:12:01.960
If you want to back out,

00:12:02.400 --> 00:12:03.840
I won't take this job.

00:12:04.080 --> 00:12:05.320
We will leave at dawn.

00:12:05.680 --> 00:12:06.410
Big Brother.

00:12:06.760 --> 00:12:08.240
There are still two bell ringers on the mountain

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.280
who haven't been paid.

00:12:09.280 --> 00:12:10.560
I'll pay for them.

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:11.490
Second Brother.

00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:12.800
Boss Chu said

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:14.160
she is the Princess of Beijing.

00:12:14.160 --> 00:12:15.360
So what if she's the Princess?

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:16.480
We are not her husbands.

00:12:16.480 --> 00:12:18.080
The second brother is right.

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:19.520
Then let's just go back home.

00:12:19.520 --> 00:12:20.040
Brother.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:21.440
That person chased us so eagerly just now.

00:12:21.440 --> 00:12:23.100
Is he after our final payment?

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:25.360
How dare you!

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:37.730
No one can enter the Lin residence uninvited.

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:39.480
This rule must be true.

00:12:40.440 --> 00:12:41.840
We can't just force our way in.

00:12:41.840 --> 00:12:42.840
There's no way.

00:12:43.800 --> 00:12:44.440
This...

00:12:44.560 --> 00:12:46.560
The reward isn't as important as our lives, right?

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:48.760
We just met, we don't have to go that far.

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:51.290
Are you not saving Xiaolan either?

00:12:51.760 --> 00:12:52.800
No.

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.600
Think of something quickly.

00:12:55.640 --> 00:12:56.640
What should we do?

00:12:59.840 --> 00:13:00.480
Wait.

00:13:01.640 --> 00:13:03.370
I told you to train your bodies.

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:05.600
Brother!

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:07.080
Brother!

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:11.200
Brother!

00:13:14.760 --> 00:13:15.560
Help!

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:20.640
It's no use.

00:13:20.640 --> 00:13:21.720
The force is too strong.

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:22.850
We can't pull you up.

00:13:24.640 --> 00:13:26.120
Leave me.

00:13:26.160 --> 00:13:28.560
Your final payments will be buried with me.

00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:30.320
I'm happy about that.

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:32.560
I've lived enough in this life.

00:13:32.560 --> 00:13:33.840
In your dreams.

00:13:33.960 --> 00:13:34.880
If you steal my money,

00:13:34.880 --> 00:13:36.810
I'll dig up your ancestral graves.

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:37.600
Do you have

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:39.130
anything he touches often?

00:13:39.160 --> 00:13:39.960
What?

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:42.120
Do you have anything he frequently touches?

00:13:42.120 --> 00:13:43.450
Frequently touches...

00:13:43.680 --> 00:13:45.960
Does Qiaoyun from Baihua Pavilion count?

00:13:45.960 --> 00:13:46.560
What is that?

00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:47.760
Prostitutes don't count.

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:48.880
Feng Buji!

00:13:48.880 --> 00:13:49.960
Liu Erzhu!

00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:52.520
Screw you both!

00:13:53.160 --> 00:13:54.960
You three are really something.

00:13:55.280 --> 00:13:56.560
Does his sword count?

00:13:56.560 --> 00:13:57.360
Yes.

00:13:57.560 --> 00:13:58.240
Liu Wancai.

00:13:58.240 --> 00:13:59.320
Bring his sword here.

00:13:59.320 --> 00:13:59.840
What are you going to do?

00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:00.480
Save him.

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:01.340
Do you trust me?

00:14:01.480 --> 00:14:02.840
Yes.

00:14:03.080 --> 00:14:04.610
I can't hold on much longer!

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:09.280
Grafting.

00:14:09.320 --> 00:14:09.960
Activate.

00:14:17.280 --> 00:14:18.480
Brother!

00:14:19.040 --> 00:14:19.720
Brother!

00:14:29.440 --> 00:14:30.920
Thank you for saving me, brother.

00:14:30.920 --> 00:14:32.000
I, Li Dashan,

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:33.720
owe you a favor.

00:14:34.520 --> 00:14:35.450
You're welcome.

00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:39.640
Brother.

00:14:40.120 --> 00:14:41.280
I won't say much.

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:43.000
My life

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:44.720
is yours from now on.

00:14:45.960 --> 00:14:46.960
Mr. Lin.

00:14:47.440 --> 00:14:49.040
You saved my brother's life.

00:14:49.160 --> 00:14:50.820
It means you saved my life too.

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:52.680
I will follow your lead.

00:14:52.720 --> 00:14:53.850
I am at your command.

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:54.680
Well,

00:14:55.240 --> 00:14:56.440
my name is Liu Erzhu.

00:14:56.640 --> 00:14:57.440
Me too.

00:14:58.520 --> 00:14:59.450
You're welcome.

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:00.940
It was nothing.

00:15:01.080 --> 00:15:02.680
It's a pity about your sword.

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:05.400
It seems this move can save a life at a critical moment.

00:15:05.400 --> 00:15:06.520
I need to practice it a few more times to get used to it.

00:15:06.520 --> 00:15:07.720
When did you learn

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:08.850
such a divine skill,

00:15:09.320 --> 00:15:11.520
and without being limited by the rules?

00:15:12.760 --> 00:15:14.520
Everyone has secrets.

00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:17.260
Why are you here alone?

00:15:17.680 --> 00:15:18.810
Where is Su Ningxue?

00:15:20.080 --> 00:15:21.120
The master...

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:22.960
she was taken away by the ghost wedding procession.

00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:23.640
You...

00:15:28.360 --> 00:15:29.690
How did you protect her?

00:15:30.040 --> 00:15:30.920
Your magic is gone.

00:15:30.920 --> 00:15:32.180
Is your brain gone too?

00:15:32.280 --> 00:15:33.360
The pharmacy owner said

00:15:33.360 --> 00:15:35.120
he knows how to enter the Lin Mansion.

00:15:35.120 --> 00:15:35.760
But

00:15:35.760 --> 00:15:37.490
he will only tell if he sees you.

00:15:43.720 --> 00:15:45.360
That's all I know.

00:15:45.760 --> 00:15:46.920
The young master and I

00:15:46.920 --> 00:15:48.960
left the Lin Mansion around the same time.

00:15:48.960 --> 00:15:50.480
I admit I took Han Xiaoying.

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:52.320
I was desperate for a wife.

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:54.040
Vulgar.

00:15:54.120 --> 00:15:56.360
You said the ghost wedding procession only takes women.

00:15:56.360 --> 00:15:58.880
Anyone else who gets close will have their life force drained.

00:15:58.880 --> 00:16:01.480
What are the rules for the funeral procession taking people?

00:16:01.480 --> 00:16:03.410
Why did they take Han Xiaoying too?

00:16:03.840 --> 00:16:05.160
I really don't know.

00:16:05.560 --> 00:16:07.720
Who knew the ghost wedding sedan wouldn't take her,

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:09.240
but the coffin would instead?

00:16:09.240 --> 00:16:10.640
Does Han Xiaoying

00:16:10.640 --> 00:16:12.900
have anything to do with the Lin Mansion?

00:16:13.040 --> 00:16:14.240
No connection at all.

00:16:14.240 --> 00:16:15.320
Is it possible?

00:16:15.880 --> 00:16:17.720
The women required for the ghost wedding

00:16:17.720 --> 00:16:19.200
must firstly be unmarried,

00:16:19.200 --> 00:16:21.260
and secondly be of marriageable age.

00:16:22.120 --> 00:16:24.520
Miss Xiaoying is obviously too young.

00:16:25.520 --> 00:16:26.760
No.

00:16:26.960 --> 00:16:29.440
Some married women were also taken away.

00:16:29.720 --> 00:16:31.680
That tree demon is over a hundred years old.

00:16:31.680 --> 00:16:33.140
Do they take them that old?

00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:35.400
There is no point discussing this now.

00:16:35.400 --> 00:16:37.800
We must hurry and find a way into the Lin Residence.

00:16:37.800 --> 00:16:39.000
I wonder if Su Ningxue

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:40.480
can hold out until dawn.

00:16:40.680 --> 00:16:41.600
Right now,

00:16:41.600 --> 00:16:43.560
the only known person who could enter the Lin Residence

00:16:43.560 --> 00:16:44.920
and come out alive

00:16:45.400 --> 00:16:46.680
is the village head's wife.

00:16:46.680 --> 00:16:48.400
She was also turned into a corpse demon.

00:16:48.400 --> 00:16:50.520
Previously, whenever ghost soldiers held a funeral in Luoxian Town,

00:16:50.520 --> 00:16:52.680
curious villagers would approach to watch.

00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:54.920
They were controlled by the soul-catching bell to enter the Lin Residence,

00:16:54.920 --> 00:16:56.080
and never came out again.

00:16:56.080 --> 00:16:58.000
So now, as soon as the sun sets,

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:00.080
the people of Luoxian Town lock their doors tightly.

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:02.010
At the time, the village head cried

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:04.599
that his wife was taken away by a coffin.

00:17:05.079 --> 00:17:08.140
Obviously, she didn't follow the soul-catching bell.

00:17:08.319 --> 00:17:11.650
The Lin Residence cannot be entered without an invitation.

00:17:12.040 --> 00:17:13.599
Perhaps the method of invitation

00:17:13.599 --> 00:17:15.530
is the sedan chair and that coffin.

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:34.880
Mother,

00:17:35.080 --> 00:17:37.440
is the Lin family here to take people again?

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:38.480
Shh.

00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.320
Don't speak.

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:40.520
Go to sleep.

00:17:40.600 --> 00:17:42.860
Everything will be fine when you wake up.

00:17:43.880 --> 00:17:44.840
I should go.

00:17:45.080 --> 00:17:46.600
After all, you're not a demon hunter.

00:17:46.600 --> 00:17:47.440
The Lin residence

00:17:47.440 --> 00:17:48.700
must be full of danger.

00:17:49.880 --> 00:17:50.480
Wait.

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:54.120
You are the last fighting force in Luoxian Town.

00:17:54.120 --> 00:17:55.880
You need to suppress the Lin residence from the front.

00:17:55.880 --> 00:17:56.440
I'll go.

00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:59.040
It must be extremely dangerous inside the Lin residence now.

00:17:59.040 --> 00:18:00.520
Aren't you afraid of ending up like the village head's wife,

00:18:00.520 --> 00:18:01.840
refined into a corpse demon?

00:18:01.840 --> 00:18:03.170
The village head's wife

00:18:03.400 --> 00:18:04.600
and Han Xiaoying

00:18:04.800 --> 00:18:06.720
must have met certain conditions

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:08.340
to be chosen by the coffin.

00:18:08.440 --> 00:18:09.040
So,

00:18:09.800 --> 00:18:10.800
I have to exploit the loophole.

